\id 2TH - Maka NT [mca] -Paraguay (web 2014)
\h 2 TESALONICENSES
\toc1 2 TESALONICENSES
\toc2 2 Tesalonicenses
\toc3 2Ts
\mt1 2 TESALONICENSES
\c 1
\s1 Yojo in mexe wetfel pa' Pablo.
\p 
\v 1 Yakha' Pablo qa na' Silvano qa na' Timoteo hika'aƚ ha'ne witfaakanek t'ejuyii hekhewe' hats yijayan ha' Cristo i'ni' ha' witset Tesalónica, ewi'ƚ i'niji' in yijayan pa' Intata qa ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo.\x * \xo 1:1 \xt Hch 15:22; 16:1; 17:1; 2Co 1:19; 1Ts 1:1; 1P 5:12; 1Ti 1:2\x*
\v 2 Na'lƚek pa' Intata qa ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo qu' net'iftits'iƚ ewets qa' neƚisi'ƚij iye pa' wit'ikesimeya'x.
\s1 Pa' Intata yitanithen hatse' pekhewe' yaqsiijkii pa' uƚ'ax.
\p 
\v 3 Yekheweli'ƚ nite' hili'iƚij in hitjiiƚijetspha'm pa' Intata ƚe'wisij qe ta'ƚi'ƚ ewets week ekheweli'ƚ, yejefets. Hats weju'ƚij in week neƚuts t'ijaifik'i pa' nite' eqekuyejeyi'ƚij ha' Yatsat'ax'inij, qa hats weju'ƚij iye in week neƚuts les qi in ƚewetsu'uni'ƚ.\x * \xo 1:3 \xt 1Co 13:1; 1Jn 4:16; Fil 2:2; 1Ts 4:10\x*
\v 4 Yekheweli'ƚ henfeljiiƚi'm hekhewe' hats yijayan ha' Cristo week he' witsetits ka' ejunyejeyi'ƚ in nite' ƚanqami'ƚij pa'nte' eqekuyejeyi'ƚij ha' Yatsat'ax'inij yemjeetax in qi in ƚ'awitjaxtiitaxi'ƚ qa qi iye in ƚawtshenhetitaxi'ƚkii iye.\x * \xo 1:4 \xt 2Co 12:5\x*
\v 5 Aka'an in enifenyejyi'ƚkii qa inq'ethinij in nite' yijanik'i pa' Intata qu' nitanithen pekhewe'en qa ekhewelƚi'iƚ qa' uyi'ƚetsji' hatse' pa' tenek'enhe'yi' pa' Intata, hikpa' ta'ƚets in qi in ƚawtshenheti'yi'ƚkii.\x * \xo 1:5 \xt 1Jn 1:9; Mt 12:41; Jn 5:22,27,30; 8:16; 16:11; He 9:27; Stg 2:13; 2P 3:7; Ap 14:7; 16:7; 19:2; Fil 1:29\x*
\v 6 Pa' Intata yatsathenik'i qu' nawtsheten hatse' pekhewe' nawitjitaxi'ƚ.
\v 7 Qa ekheweli'ƚ in qi in ƚ'awitjaxti'yi'ƚ qa qi qu' mawapiyi'ƚ hatse' qa yekheweli'ƚ qa' ha'ni'ƚ etji'teje'm iye. Aka'an ƚunye'jkii hatse' qu' ne'twenhetiitaxjipha'm na' wa's ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesús qa pe' t'units angelits qa pa' qi fe't iye,
\v 8 ma' qa' netisij pakha' weju'ƚij pekhewe' nite' nikfe'lets pa' Dios qa nite' tek'enik'i iye ke' ƚe'lijei ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo.\x * \xo 1:8 \xt 1Co 3:13; He 10:27; 12:29; 2P 3:7; Ap 14:10; Sal 79:6; Is 66:15; Jer 10:25; 1P 4:17\x*
\v 9 Pekhewe'en nite' yili'ij qu' qi qu' naats'e' pakha' weju'ƚij qu' namii, qi qu' toxi' imiiha ha' Yatsat'ax'inij qa' nite' ni'wene' iye pa' qi ƚe'wis tujji' ta'ƚets pa' ƚet'unha'x.\x * \xo 1:9 \xt 1Ti 6:9; Gn 4:14; Is 2:10,19,21\x*
\v 10 Ha' Yatsat'ax'inij qu' netpiltaxju' hatse' hats'inha inekhewel in jitajayan qa' qi qu' jintiwqinhetji' qa' qiyi'ija iye qu' jinteqenij hatse'. Ekheweli'ƚ ƚa'ni'ƚ ji'teje'm hatse' pekhewe'en qe nite' ƚeqeku'uƚik'i kekhewe' henfeli'ƚ.\x * \xo 1:10 \xt Mr 8:38; Jn 17:10; Ro 8:17; Ef 5:3; 6:18\x*
\v 11 Qa hik ta'ƚijupi' in nite' hili'iƚij in k'iyini'ƚ epji'kii week ƚahatsiyij hats'inha in hats t'eku'mi'ƚ eiji'kii pa' Intata qa'nte' aqsi'ji'iƚijkii pa' uƚ'ax. Hats'inha iye qa' neƚisi'ƚij pa'qu' et'unhaxitsi'iƚijup qu' aqsi'ji'ƚijkii pa' yisu'un, qe ekheweli'ƚ ƚ'ek'eni'ƚets.\x * \xo 1:11 \xt Ef 4:1; Col 3:15; Ga 2:16; 1Ts 1:3\x*
\v 12 Ma' qa' olots pe'qu' niwqinhetji' ka' ƚii ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo qe ta'ƚi'ƚ ewets qa ekheweli'ƚ qa' newqinheti'ƚji' iye qe ta'ƚets in ƚijayani'ƚ ha' Yatsat'ax'inij. Ekewe'en week qu' nata'ƚets pa' ƚeqi'fenkeye'j inij pa' Intata qa ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo.\x * \xo 1:12 \xt Jn 13:31; 14:13; Hch 3:16; 15:14; Fil 2:10; Is 24:15; 49:3; 66:5; Mal 1:11; 2Co 8:23\x*
\c 2
\s1 Qu' netpiltaxju' pa' Yatsat'ax'inij.
\p 
\v 1 Yejefets, hane'ej qu' k'efeli'ƚi'm pa' ƚunye'j qu' netpiltaxju' ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo qa pa' ƚunye'j iye qu' ewi'ƚ ji'nentaxi', k'iyini'ƚij ewets\x * \xo 2:1 \xt 1Ts 1:10; 1Jn 2:28; Ap 11:8\x*
\v 2 qu' hasu'uj qu' aje'eƚ enƚ'ilaxi'ƚ qu' impi'ye'eƚij qu' hats netpilju' pa'aj ha' Yatsat'ax'inij qu' nata'ƚets espirituye' in ƚ'impi'ye'eƚij i'nƚi'i qu' nata'ƚets pe'qu' wi'tlijeye' qa i'nƚi'i qu' nata'ƚets pa'qu' witfaakanek'e qu' netitijitiyijets qu' nata'ƚi'ƚ yiwets.\x * \xo 2:2 \xt 1Jn 2:28; 4:1; Mt 25:13; Hch 2:20; Fil 1:6; 2Ti 2:18\x*
\v 3 Hasu'uj qu' nawitji'iƚij pe'ye' aka'an, qe yojo qu' olootse' pe'qu' nili'ij ha' Yatsat'ax'inij qa qu' ne'twenhetii pa' jukhew uƚ'ax ƚeiƚe', hikpa' hats jutsiqax qu' nattanithenhetii hatse'. Ma' qa hats netpilju' ha' Yatsat'ax'inij.
\v 4 Ma' qa' ink'aye'ƚe pa' jukhew uƚ'ax ƚeiƚe' qa' naqsiijkii qu' qi qu' netnek'enhei qa' net'ejuyiju'ƚ week pekhewe' wenit'ijets qu' diositse' qa pa' Intata iye, qa' ƚ'ejuihifetsi'ij iye week pe' wekwek yejutshenets pe'qu' ƚoqodiositse' qa pe' t'ejuyets iye pa' Intata. Ma' qa' nuyifi pe' qi witlijtsitjii t'ejuyets pa' Intata qa' na'nipji' pa' witts'oji'la'x. Qa' nit'ij ƚetets qu' ƚakha'ye' pa' Dioosija.\x * \xo 2:4 \xt 1Co 8:5; Is 14:12-15; Ez 28:2; Hch 17:23\x*
\v 5 ¿Me nite' ƚantapi'iƚik'i aka'an in hayiits k'efeli'ƚi'm in mexe ha'ni'ƚ etji'teje'm?
\v 6 Ekheweli'ƚ hats ƚenikfe'li'ƚets pa' mexe niyejinik'ui ipƚu'ui qu' namets pa' ƚahats'ij qu' netesti'yij ma' qa' ne'twenhetii pa' jukhew uƚ'ax ƚeiƚe'.\x * \xo 2:6 \xt Lc 21:8\x*
\v 7 Qe pa' ham nikfe'le'ets uƚ'ax qu' ƚunye'je'kii hatse', hats i'nju' hane'ej hats ewi'ƚƚe in hamik'ui qu' netenifte'ji' pa' mexe yothetiju'ƚ.\x * \xo 2:7 \xt Mt 13:41\x*
\v 8 Ma' qa' hayitse' qa' ne'twenhetii pa' jukhew uƚ'ax ƚeiƚe'. Qa ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesús qa' nifuyu'ets qa' uƚ'axe'ju' pa' uƚ'ax ƚeiƚe' qa pa' qi koojo ta'ƚets qu' nente'nilitju' ha' Jesús qa' niwuƚ'enhetju' iye pa' uƚ'ax ƚeiƚe'.\x * \xo 2:8 \xt Is 11:4; 30:28\x*
\v 9 Ha'ne jukhew uƚ'ax ƚeiƚe' ƚeq'ithayinenek pa' Satanás qi qu' net'un qu' netnek'enhei qa naqsiijkii iye pe' ham ƚunyejeyiju'ƚ qa nite'ƚe yijaalija yisu'unƚe qu' nawitji ene' sehe' epji' qa qi qu' nitjuƚaxiƚijpha'mkii.\x * \xo 2:9 \xt Mt 24:24; Mr 13:22; Ap 13:13\x*
\v 10 Qi qu' nawitji'iji' pe' wekwek pekhewe' hats jutsiqets qu' namii pa' fe't qe enewe'en nite' yisu'un pa' yijaataxija qekha iƚiye'tax.\x * \xo 2:10 \xt Hch 16:30; Ef 2:8\x*
\v 11 Qa hik ta'ƚijupi' pa' Intata qu' niwejinij qu' nawitji pa' qi witwejtitsi' pekhewe'en, qa qi qu' numti qu' yijaayi'ija.
\v 12 Ma' qa i'nk'aƚe qa' nitanithen week pekhewe' nite' tek'enets pa' yijaataxija qe ƚekhewel yisu'unji' pa' uƚ'ax.\x * \xo 2:12 \xt Jn 5:22-30; 6:64\x*
\s1 Pa'n ƚunye'j pa'qu' naqsiijkii pekhewe' hats yijayan pa' Jesús.
\p 
\v 13 Qa yekheweli'ƚ les ƚe'wis qu' hit'iƚijetspha'mkii ƚe'wisij pa' Intata qe ta'ƚi'ƚ ewets. Yejefets ha' Yatsat'ax'inij nesu'uni'ƚ qe pa' Intata hayiits t'eku'mi'ƚ eiji'kii pa'aj qe qa' i'ƚiyi'iƚ qu' nata'ƚets pa' Espíritu Santo qa pa' nite' eqekuyejyi'ƚij pa' yijaa'ija.\x * \xo 2:13 \xt Ro 6:19; 9:11; 11:5; Ef 1:4; 1Ts 1:4; 4:3; 1Co 1:30; 1Ti 2:15; He 12:14; 1P 1:2\x*
\v 14 Aka'an hik aka' ƚunyee'jkiiha qa in yamets in taya'yi'ƚ ewets pa' Intata qa i'nijji' ekewe' henfeli'ƚ qe qa' ami'ƚets hatse' pa' qi ƚesa'x ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo.\x * \xo 2:14 \xt Lc 9:32; Jn 17:24; 2Co 3:18; 1P 5:1,4; 2P 3:18\x*
\v 15 Qa hik ta'ƚijupi' yejefets, ment'unheti'ƚ. Anqamkite'eƚij kekhewe' hats k'ijatsheniƚij in mexe ha'ni'ƚ etji'teje'm qa kekhewe' hika'aƚ e'm iye.\x * \xo 2:15 \xt Ro 14:4; 1Co 16:13; Fil 1:27; Mr 7:3; 1Ti 4:11; Jud 3\x*
\v 16 Ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo hik hakhaa'ija, qa pakha' iye Intata Dios, pakha' jiyisu'un, pakha' jiyeƚisij in nite' yili'ij in ikesimen pe' intawjets qa pa' inwetjumtikineye'jik'ui iye pe' jiyeƚisij hatse' ta'ƚets pa' ƚeqi'fenkeye'j,\x * \xo 2:16 \xt Jn 3:16; Ap 12:11\x*
\v 17 qu' hik enewe'ye' qu' nisimetsin qa' nakakƚin iye pe' atawjetsi'ƚ qa' naqsiijkii iye qu' net'ijaifik'i pa' ƚe'wis ithayijkit'iƚ qa eke' wi'tlijei ƚe'sits in ƚenfeli'ƚ.
\c 3
\s1 Pablo qa iyinets qu' netniyinhe'yipjikii.
\p 
\v 1 Hatse', ewi'ƚƚi'ijha aka' qu' hit'iƚij ewets iye. Yejefets, iyini'ƚyipji'kii hats'inha eke' ƚe'lijei ha' Yatsat'ax'inij qa'nte' optoxe' qu' week nenikfe'lets qa' qi iye qu' niwqinhetji' pe'qu' uja'xe' in ejunyejeyi'ƚek in i'nk'aa ƚenikfe'li'ƚets qa ƚiwqinheti'ƚji'.\x * \xo 3:1 \xt 1Ts 2:13\x*
\v 2 Iyini'ƚyipji'kii iye hats'inha qa' netswejinjiiƚik'uifik'i pe' nite' yatsathen qa uƚ'ets iye jukhew qe nite' week qu' nisu'un qu' nijayan ha' Jesús.\x * \xo 3:2 \xt Mt 27:43; Ro 15:31\x*
\v 3 Qa ha' Yatsat'ax'inij nite' yi'tƚi'ijkii pa'qu' hats nit'ij qa yaqsiijkii. Qa hik ta'ƚijupi' ƚakha' qu' neƚisi'ƚij et'unhaxitsi'iƚ qa' netweyiju'ƚ iye pa' inwo'met Satanás.\x * \xo 3:3 \xt Mt 5:37; 6:13; 13:19,38; Jn 17:15; Ef 6:16; 1Jn 2:13-14; 3:12; 5:18-19\x*
\v 4 Yekheweli'ƚ tsikfe'li'ƚets ha' Yatsat'ax'inij qu' naqsi'ji'ƚ e'mijkii aka'an qe qa'nte' iliyi'iƚij qu' aqsiiƚijkii kekhewe' hats k'ayaji'iƚijets.
\v 5 Ha' Yatsat'ax'inij qu' nijatsheni'ƚij qu' ineqsu'uni'ƚ qu' hik ƚunye'je' pa' Intata in qi in jiyisu'un, qa' nijatsheni'ƚij iye qu'nte' itaqsuni'iƚijup pe'ye' in ƚunye'jek ha' Cristo.\x * \xo 3:5 \xt Ro 15:5; Ap 13:10\x*
\s1 Ƚe'wis qu' ji'nt'ithayii.
\p 
\v 6 Yejefets, aka' ƚiiji' ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo k'ayaji'iƚijets qu' me'nitoni'ƚi'mets week pa'qu' ƚunye'je' pekhewe' nite' ƚe'wisijupi' pa' yaqsiijkii in hats yijayantax ha' Jesús qa nite' iye yaqsiijkii kekhewe' hats k'ijatsheni'ƚij.\x * \xo 3:6 \xt Jn 14:13; Hch 3:16; 15:14; Fil 2:10; Mt 18:17; 1Co 5:11; 2Ti 3:5; 2Jn 10; Mr 7:3; Jud 3\x*
\v 7 Ekheweli'ƚ hats ƚenikfe'li'ƚetsha in les ƚe'wis qu' ojonketiƚik'i aka' yijunyejeyi'ƚ. Yekheweli'ƚ nite' haqsiiƚijkii pa'qu' uƚ'axe' in mexe ha'ni'ƚ etji'teje'mkii.\x * \xo 3:7 \xt 3Jn 11\x*
\v 8 Yekheweli'ƚ nite' hetujƚi'iƚ pe'qu' aqatsi'iƚ qu'nte' hijanini'iƚ. Yekheweli'ƚ qi in heyithayi'yi'ƚ neƚuts qa najai hats'inha qa ham pa'qu' hipekhelinheti'ƚkii.
\v 9 Yijaa'ija in ƚeke'tax qu' nek'iyini'ƚij ewets qu' etsi'feni'ƚij pe'ye' qa hisu'unƚi'iƚ qu' k'ethini'ƚij pe'ye' hats'inha qu' ojonketiƚik'i.\x * \xo 3:9 \xt Mr 1:22; Hch 9:14; Ro 13:1; 1Co 9:4-14; He 8:5\x*
\v 10 Qe yekheweli'ƚ in mexe ha'ni'ƚ etji'teje'm qa hit'iƚij ewets: —Pakha' qu'nte' nenithayiyuye' qa qantejeek neteke'.—\x * \xo 3:10 \xt 1Ts 4:11\x*
\v 11 Qe k'iye'eƚij ekheweli'ƚ in na'l pe' nite' ƚe'wisijupi' pa' yaqsiijkii. Nite' nithayiyu' ham yaqsi'ji'ijkii. Qa yijalki'sƚekii yithayimetenƚe pe'ye'.\x * \xo 3:11 \xt 1Ti 5:13\x*
\v 12 Aka' ƚiiji' ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo yekheweli'ƚ hit'iƚijets in nite' hili'iƚij qu' hakakƚini'ƚ pekhewe' nite' nithayiyu', qa qu' net'ithayii ƚe'wis qu' nenithayimetsinƚe hats'inha qu' ƚaaqi'ija pa'qu' netuj.
\v 13 Qa ekheweli'ƚ, yejefets, hasu'uj eniwefi'ƚju' in ƚaqsiiƚijkii pa' ƚe'wis.\x * \xo 3:13 \xt Lc 18:1; 2Co 4:1,16; Ga 6:9; Ef 3:13\x*
\v 14 Qu' nana'l pa'qu' ewi'ƚe' in nite' neqjunutaxij ekewe' wi'tlijei hika'aƚ e'm, maxtayitiƚij. Hasu'uj eneqjunu'uƚetskii hats'inha qa' newepinkii.
\v 15 Qa hasu'ujƚe qu' hik ƚunye'je' qu' ejuihifeyi'iƚij. Enfeli'ƚi'm yijat'ij qu' nili'ij pa' uƚ'ax hik eqfenyejeyi'iƚij pa'qu' ejefeeyi'iƚha.
\v 16 Ha' Yatsat'axij pa' wit'ikesimeya'x hik hakhaa'ija qu' neƚisi'ƚij pa' wit'ikesimeya'x week ƚahatsiyij pa'qu'ƚe niyi'iƚi'. Ha' Yatsat'ax'inij qu' na'ni'ƚ etji'ju'.\x * \xo 3:16 \xt 1Ts 5:23; Nm 6:26; Ef 6:23; Ro 15:33; 1Co 16:24; 2Co 13:13; Tit 3:15; He 13:25\x*
\s1 Wetfel pa' Pablo.
\p 
\v 17 Yakha' Pablo. Yakhaa'ija in hika' ha'ne ƚ'aka'the'ju' ha'ne witfaakanek. Aka'an hik aka' yeqfenye'j ji'jij week ke' yifaakanhei. Enewe'en yeq'ikatii.\x * \xo 3:17 \xt 1Co 16:21\x*
\v 18 Na'lƚek ha' Yatsat'ax'inij Jesucristo qu' net'iftits'iƚ ewets week ekheweli'ƚ. Amén.
